<html5>
  <!--

    Information:

    Every CSS below this marker should be easely reusable
    The structure is simple, every tag represent a real tag in the final html output

    name: Supported tags are style, script and link
    output: if yes, output the tag in the html head, if false, the file will only send to ouput
    filename: the final filename
    prefix: used to add IE conditional comments
    suffix: same as previous
    attributes: define all attributes you want to have in the tag
    value: direct content to be output, use CDATA
    source: list of file to be concatenated and compressed
    -->

